flowchart LR
    I1[Current Available Inventory by Group] --> C1[Compute 30-Day Average Consumption]
    C1 --> C2[Projected Stock Days = Current / Daily Rate]
    C2 --> C3{Projected Days < 3?}
    C3 -->|Yes| A1[Create Shortage Alert]
    C3 -->|No| A2[No Alert]
    A1 --> D1[Fetch Eligible Donors by Group]
    D1 --> D2[Rank by Donations and Days Since Last]
    D2 --> O1[Display Suggested Donors on Dashboard]
